    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="a28d5-101">使用組態檔中 ASP.NET <see langword="&lt;machineKey&gt;" /> 元素指定的簽署和加密金鑰，處理工作階段權杖。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="a28d5-101">Processes session tokens by using signing and encryption keys specified in the ASP.NET <see langword="&lt;machineKey&gt;" /> element in a configuration file.</span>
      </span>
